<P>
<a name="privacy"></a>
<B>Our Commitment To Your Privacy And Security</B>
</P>

<P>
Produce Reporter Co. takes your privacy very seriously.  Our policy is to respect and protect the privacy of the businesses and individuals that use our web site.  Our relationship with you is our most valuable asset and is the very basis of our reputation and name, first established in 1901.
</P>

<P>
We provide this Privacy Statement to explain our online information policies and security practices.  It describes how we collect and use information on this web site, and the choices that you can make about the way your information is collected and used.  So that this Privacy Statement is easy to find, we make it available via a link at the bottom of our homepage.
</P>

<P>
By providing the information requested by Produce Reporter Co.'s online forms and by continuing to use this web site after having had an opportunity to review this Privacy Statement, you have consented to Produce Reporter Co.'s use of the information it collects as described at the point of collection or in this Privacy Statement.  This Privacy Statement should be read and understood in association with the Terms and Conditions and/or other electronic or written agreements between you and Produce Reporter Co. governing the terms and conditions of your use of this web site and/or Produce Reporter Co.'s software, databases, products or services.
</P>

<P>
Produce Reporter Co. reserves the right to review and revise this Privacy Statement from time to time without giving you prior notice.  For this reason, we encourage you to review this Privacy Statement whenever you use this web site.  Your use of the web site following any such modification constitutes your agreement to follow and be bound by the Privacy Statement as modified.  The last date this Privacy Statement was modified is set forth below.
</P>

