<P>
<a name="data"></a>
<B>Our Commitment To Data Security</B>
</P>

<P>
To prevent unauthorized access, maintain data integrity, and ensure the correct use of information, Produce Reporter Co. has put in place physical, electronic, and managerial procedures to safeguard and secure the information we collect.  For instance, credit card payment information is processed and protected by VeriSign, Inc., our online payment services partner through use of a secure billing system.  Both Produce Reporter Co. and VeriSign use various security measures to protect against unauthorized access to your credit card information including firewalls, encryption, and secure servers.  Neither Produce Reporter Co. nor VeriSign use or voluntarily share credit card information for any other purpose than described herein.
</P>

<P>
Please be aware, however, that no Internet-based computer system can be considered 100% safe from intrusion.  By accessing and using this web site, you agree that you, and not Produce Reporter Co., shall bear the risk of any use or misuse of your information that is obtained by "hacking" or other nefarious means.
</P>

