<a name="use"></a>
<B>The Way We Use The Information We Collect</B>
</P>

<P>
We limit the collection of information to what is necessary to administer our business and to deliver superior service to you, and we use the information provided in ways that are compatible with the purposes for which it is gathered.  For example, we will use the information you provide about yourself or your business to process your requests and transactions, and to supply you with additional information about products and services.
</P>

<P>
The trading experience information you provide on other businesses or individuals is received, and protected, by us in confidence.  We understand, and take very seriously, our responsibility not to disclose the source of any confidential trading experience report provided to Produce Reporter Co. on another business. These reports are used for the purposes of ensuring that Blue Book listings, ratings, and related products and services are as reliable as possible.
</P>

